        Engineers and procurement teams are using AI assistants to shortlist suppliers, compare specifications, and verify compliance credentials — before they visit a single manufacturer website.
        <strong class="text-white">GEO for manufacturing</strong> is the discipline of making your technical product content, specification data, and distributor network discoverable and citable in the AI-generated answers that shape specification decisions.
